body.p:
Covalently connected donor-acceptor molecules are designed and tuned to attain charge-transfer-mediated structural rearrangements, which manifests solvatochromic effects to be used for various applications1–4. Merocyanine dyes with donor-(π\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
