				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$^{-1}$$\end{document}, possibly represents aromatic ring stretching vibrations or the vibrational mode of cyclohexane) to the electronic transition (S0→S1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
